document_data.mainbody:
ldathyn was a small tree city found within Duskwood Dell in Amn.
Alatoasz Berendim, the Most Exalted Fallskeeper of Eldaths sacred Duskwood Dell, was a prominent inhabitant of Eldathyn. Since Alatoasz trained priests of Eldath he was the leader of Eldathyn for all intents and purposes.
